Sogefi SpA (SO)  is looking to invest in
Brazil and  China ,  Milano Finanza  reported, without saying where
it got the information.  Sogefi aims to invest in car-parts production and
distribution, the weekly newspaper reported. contracts in the
U.S., the weekly newspaper said. Sogefi may sign an agreement
with General Motors Co., which is already its client in  Europe .  To contact the reporter on this story:
